{"tid":1684194,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)萬聖節特別節目","createTime":"2019-10-31T03:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T15:15:00.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ea7b1b1df06403a6bdebcb28e8cc87a9672c1641","tid":1684194,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:29:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啊~~~死黑警~~~又唔做嘢又唔讀書</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=e8f31ab1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=7ecc5728\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=13f74cb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/10/The_Cabin_in_the_Woods.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F10%2FThe_Cabin_in_the_Woods.jpg&h=213436b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7a/Hansel_and_Gretel-_Witch_Hunters_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F7a%2FHansel_and_Gretel-_Witch_Hunters_Poster.jpg&h=61ccf1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3804/d3804151.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3804%2Fd3804151.jpg&h=7204564f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/55/Van_Helsing_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F55%2FVan_Helsing_poster.jpg&h=b72c2fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images2.fanpop.com/images/photos/2800000/Freddy-vs-Jason-freddy-krueger-2835423-1280-1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages2.fanpop.com%2Fimages%2Fphotos%2F2800000%2FFreddy-vs-Jason-freddy-krueger-2835423-1280-1024.jpg&h=3dad5c57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/dc/Trick_r_treat.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fd%2Fdc%2FTrick_r_treat.jpg&h=3a0bfbd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事講述五名青年男女去森林度假屋遊玩，可是卻遇上恐怖血腥事件，遊玩變成被虐殺，但其實這並不是一間普通房屋。正當他們真真正正發現了問題時，事情早就向著超乎想像的方向發展⋯⋯而最後的真相，更癲覆了他們對於這個世界的認知⋯⋯ <br />\n<br />\n2.構思自家喻戶曉的格林童話「糖果屋」。「糖果屋」故事發生後的15年，韓賽爾與葛蕾特這對兄妹成為了所向無敵的獎金獵人，專門消滅世界各地的女巫<br />\n<br />\n3.在人間之外的天堂與地獄之戰綿延不絕，雙方都在為自己爭取強力的戰士。中情局特工西蒙斯（邁克爾&middot;加&middot;懷特Michael Jai White 飾）厭倦了殺戮的任務，向上司威恩（馬丁&middot;辛Martin Sheen 飾）提出退出，豈料卻在朝鮮執行任務時被威恩害死。墜入地獄的西蒙斯與惡魔馬里波吉亞達成協議，同意為它統率地獄軍隊來換得再生報仇的機會。被惡魔雪藏五年的西蒙斯再生回到人間....<br />\n<br />\n4.凡赫辛為教會委託獵殺異種魔物的獵人，於接受教會委託協助一家族對抗吸血殭屍，之後捲入狼人、科學怪人和德古拉間的風波&hellip;結果竟發現此項任務似乎是命運對其身世的安排&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n5.猛鬼街片中的主角變態殺手弗萊迪由於被人忘卻，沒有人記得他也就沒有人恐懼他，為了重獲力量，他找到了一個臭名昭著變態殺手，一個帶著冰球面具而且從來不開口說話的傑森(肯&middot;克辛格)，他喜歡用一把彎刀肢解小孩子， 弗萊迪利用他的特長進入傑森的夢中，利用傑森母親的形象控制他，命令他到榆樹街上殺人，這樣弗萊迪才能重新得到復生的力量，被喚醒的傑森來到榆樹街大開殺戒，當地陷入一片恐慌，以前的孩子們再次陷入弗萊迪的噩夢，然後夢中弗萊迪要殺戮的人頭卻不巧被傑森搶先搶走，弗萊迪大怒決定進入傑森的夢境幹掉傑森，於是兩個頂級變態殺手的終極對決就此展...<br />\n<br />\n6.以《鬼作秀》與《魔界奇談》的敘事方式呈現四起發生在萬聖節晚上的恐怖事件：一位高中校長（狄倫貝克飾）到了夜晚就變成兇猛的連續殺人犯；一位年輕處女（安娜佩恩飾）尋找讓自己變身的特別人物；一群青少年的殘忍惡作劇卻帶來悲慘的後果；一位性情乖戾的老人（布萊恩考克斯飾）與淘氣的萬聖節惡魔交戰<br />\n<br />\n1 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=0d2257bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=bb1b2d00\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07157536e71a915a98638f9f71d7d67b196b5f0d","tid":1684194,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00878f0aeb116731a1ddbe6391b92589a0384328","tid":1684194,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8291a753599b71872f005fc53d6e04c71ff35e4","tid":1684194,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" 